00:12:49,721 --> 00:12:52,657
-Wait a minute!

272
00:12:52,690 --> 00:12:53,658
Proton cell!

273
00:12:53,691 --> 00:12:55,026
Avalanche axis!

274
00:13:00,231 --> 00:13:02,534
-How's that feel?

275
00:13:02,567 --> 00:13:03,635
-Ah.

276
00:13:03,668 --> 00:13:06,638
How refreshing.

277
00:13:06,671 --> 00:13:08,873
My turn.

278
00:13:08,940 --> 00:13:11,176
-Oh no!

279
00:13:11,176 --> 00:13:13,411
-Thanks.

280
00:13:13,445 --> 00:13:15,647
We'll need more than that
to beat this guy.

281
00:13:15,680 --> 00:13:17,182
Now stay back.

282
00:13:17,248 --> 00:13:18,750
I'm going to try something that
could get a bit messy.

283
00:13:18,783 --> 00:13:20,018
-Hey, don't worry about me.

284
00:13:20,018 --> 00:13:21,386
I'll be right here.

285
00:13:21,386 --> 00:13:23,588
-Yeah, I'm OK with that.

286
00:13:23,621 --> 00:13:25,056
-Koji, back me up.

287
00:13:25,090 --> 00:13:28,226
-No prob.

288
00:13:28,259 --> 00:13:29,561
-Solar wind destroyer!

289
00:13:37,902 --> 00:13:39,204
-Game over.

290
00:13:42,740 --> 00:13:44,909
[evil laughter]

291
00:13:44,909 --> 00:13:47,212
-Man, I've got to work
on my serve.

292
00:13:47,245 --> 00:13:48,413
-Next.

293
00:13:48,413 --> 00:13:49,047
-That's it.

294
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,315
I've had enough.

295
00:13:50,348 --> 00:13:51,883
Frozen hunter!

296
00:13:57,655 --> 00:13:59,157
That did it.

297
00:13:59,190 --> 00:14:00,158
-Indeed.

298
00:14:00,191 --> 00:14:03,761
It showed just how
pathetic you are.

299
00:14:03,795 --> 00:14:05,630
-What's with this guy?

300
00:14:05,663 --> 00:14:09,434
-Shall I destroy you now or do
you want to play some more?

301
00:14:09,467 --> 00:14:12,137
-We'd better think of something
quick or he's going

302
00:14:12,137 --> 00:14:12,804
to squash us like a bunch
of little beetles.

303
00:14:12,804 --> 00:14:13,805
-Great.

304
00:14:13,805 --> 00:14:15,673
Thanks a lot for
that visual, Z.

305
00:14:15,740 --> 00:14:16,941
-You had your chance.

306
00:14:16,975 --> 00:14:17,976
My turn.

307
00:14:22,580 --> 00:14:25,149
-What is he doing?

308
00:14:25,216 --> 00:14:29,187
-Form of judgment.

309
00:14:29,187 --> 00:14:33,124
[screams]

310
00:14:33,191 --> 00:14:34,192
-Koichi!

311
00:14:49,040 --> 00:14:50,375
-Is he alive?

312
00:14:50,408 --> 00:14:51,175
Koichi?

313
00:14:51,209 --> 00:14:52,243
-Never felt better.

314
00:14:52,310 --> 00:14:53,378
[groans]

315
00:14:56,881 --> 00:15:00,718
-Do you suppose he'd
want a rematch?

316
00:15:00,718 --> 00:15:02,587
-Well, I'm disappointed.

317
00:15:02,620 --> 00:15:06,090
I expected at least a shred
of challenge today.

318
00:15:06,090 --> 00:15:09,027
And you, how pathetic
losing to them.

319
00:15:09,093 --> 00:15:10,261
-I'm glad.

320
00:15:10,261 --> 00:15:10,762
-Koichi!

321
00:15:10,795 --> 00:15:11,930
Don't!

322
00:15:11,963 --> 00:15:13,731
-I lost when I listened
to you.

323
00:15:13,765 --> 00:15:15,567
You made me fight
my own brother.

324
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,768
-It was your choice.

325
00:15:16,768 --> 00:15:18,403
Isn't that what you wanted?

326
00:15:18,436 --> 00:15:19,237
-No!

327
00:15:19,270 --> 00:15:20,405
You lied to me.

328
00:15:20,438 --> 00:15:21,639
You used me.

329
00:15:21,706 --> 00:15:23,441
-You're wrong.

330
00:15:23,474 --> 00:15:25,276
I merely set the stage.

331
00:15:25,276 --> 00:15:29,013
The spirit of darkness
chooses its owner.

332
00:15:29,047 --> 00:15:32,784
To be selected, one must possess
a very dark heart.

333
00:15:32,850 --> 00:15:35,820
Otherwise, the spirit's
powers are useless.

334
00:15:35,853 --> 00:15:39,090
I offered it to many before you,
but the spirit rejected

335
00:15:39,157 --> 00:15:41,426
them one after another.

336
00:15:41,492 --> 00:15:44,529
The power of darkness is
your destiny, Koichi.

337
00:15:44,562 --> 00:15:45,964
It's where you belong.

338
00:15:45,997 --> 00:15:51,002
Accept it and be my
servant once more.

339
00:15:51,002 --> 00:15:52,804
You've only tasted
a fraction of the

340
00:15:52,837 --> 00:15:54,672
great power of darkness.

341
00:15:54,706 --> 00:15:55,974
I'll teach you everything.

342
00:15:59,544 --> 00:16:00,845
Time to choose.

343
00:16:00,912 --> 00:16:04,349
What's it going to be, Koichi?

344
00:16:04,415 --> 00:16:05,483
-Don't listen to him!

345
00:16:05,516 --> 00:16:05,984
He's lying!

346
00:16:06,017 --> 00:16:07,352
-No, it's true.

347
00:16:07,418 --> 00:16:10,321
My heart was filled with anger
and jealousy and darkness

348
00:16:10,388 --> 00:16:12,390
became the only comfort
from my pain.

349
00:16:17,395 --> 00:16:18,596
[evil laughter]

350
00:16:18,630 --> 00:16:22,100
-But that's in the past.

351
00:16:22,133 --> 00:16:23,901
I don't want revenge anymore.

352
00:16:23,901 --> 00:16:25,103
I'm done hiding in the dark.

353
00:16:32,343 --> 00:16:35,046
I'd rather die than
betray my brother.

354
00:16:35,079 --> 00:16:37,048
-Hm, so be it.

355
00:16:44,981 --> 00:16:46,082
Koichi!

356
00:16:58,794 --> 00:17:01,097
The spirits of darkness
are changing.

357
00:17:06,469 --> 00:17:09,438
A D-Tector!

358
00:17:09,438 --> 00:17:11,073
Koichi!

359
00:17:11,107 --> 00:17:15,011
I can feel it-- the
power of darkness.

360
00:17:15,044 --> 00:17:17,013
But it's different now.

361
00:17:17,046 --> 00:17:19,415
It doesn't have to be evil.

362
00:17:19,482 --> 00:17:20,583
The pain is gone.

363
00:17:20,650 --> 00:17:22,318
I'm not afraid anymore.

364
00:17:22,351 --> 00:17:25,855
-He has discovered the
spirit's true power.

365
00:17:25,888 --> 00:17:27,156
-Yeah.

366
00:17:38,701 --> 00:17:40,002
Execute spirit evolution.

367
00:18:02,591 --> 00:18:04,560
-I'm having trouble
keeping up here.

368
00:18:04,593 --> 00:18:06,595
Didn't he used to be Duskmon?

369
00:18:06,662 --> 00:18:07,396
-He used to be.

370
00:18:07,430 --> 00:18:09,065
Now he's a completely new one.

371
00:18:13,736 --> 00:18:15,237
-Impossible!

372
00:18:15,237 --> 00:18:18,140
Somehow you've awakened the
true power of darkness.

373
00:18:22,478 --> 00:18:23,779
-Shadow meteor.

374
00:18:29,452 --> 00:18:30,753
Shadow meteor.

375
00:18:34,023 --> 00:18:36,292
Keep it going, Loweemon.

376
00:18:40,629 --> 00:18:41,931
-This nightmare's over.

377
00:18:45,401 --> 00:18:46,435
-Lightning spear!

378
00:18:54,310 --> 00:18:58,280
-Loweemon slide evolution,
JagerLoweemon.

379
00:19:04,220 --> 00:19:06,555
Prepare to be illuminated.

380
00:19:06,589 --> 00:19:10,192
Ebony blast!

381
00:19:10,192 --> 00:19:13,195
How does the darkness
taste now?

382
00:19:21,537 --> 00:19:22,838
Dark master!

383
00:19:30,112 --> 00:19:33,015
[groans]

384
00:19:33,082 --> 00:19:34,416
-He did it!

385
00:19:34,416 --> 00:19:35,451
-Sure did.

386
00:19:35,484 --> 00:19:36,519
-Wait!

387
00:19:36,585 --> 00:19:37,620
Something's wrong.

388
00:19:37,653 --> 00:19:39,121
-Huh?

389
00:19:39,155 --> 00:19:41,123
-He's dissolving but I don't
see a fractal code .

390
00:19:44,293 --> 00:19:46,262
-That wasn't the real Cherubimon
we were fighting.

391
00:19:46,295 --> 00:19:48,097
It was like some kind
of projection.

392
00:19:48,130 --> 00:19:49,932
Unfortunately, he's still
very much alive.

393
00:19:49,965 --> 00:19:52,401
I can feel him.

394
00:19:52,435 --> 00:19:54,937
-If that was just a projection,
I don't think I

395
00:19:54,937 --> 00:19:56,939
want to meet the real one.

396
00:19:56,939 --> 00:19:58,507
-You have impressed
me, Koichi.

397
00:19:58,541 --> 00:20:01,444
Awakening the true spirit of
darkness is no small feat.

398
00:20:01,510 --> 00:20:05,414
But make no mistake, you'll
never be a match for me.

399
00:20:05,481 --> 00:20:07,483
I look forward to meeting
you in person at the

400
00:20:07,516 --> 00:20:10,820
Rose Morning Star.

401
00:20:10,853 --> 00:20:11,821
-Wait!

402
00:20:11,821 --> 00:20:12,955
What are you doing?

403
00:20:12,988 --> 00:20:14,156
-I have to face him alone.

404
00:20:14,156 --> 00:20:15,624
You guys should just leave.

405
00:20:15,658 --> 00:20:16,492
-Sorry, bro.

406
00:20:16,492 --> 00:20:18,294
I can't let you do that.

407
00:20:18,327 --> 00:20:19,829
The only thing that can
defeat him is the

408
00:20:19,862 --> 00:20:21,130
true power of darkness.

409
00:20:21,163 --> 00:20:22,798
You'll only be in the way.

410
00:20:22,832 --> 00:20:24,533
-I have to help.

411
00:20:24,600 --> 00:20:26,702
True darkness must depend
on the light.

412
00:20:26,769 --> 00:20:28,304
-Sorry, but I'm going, too.

413
00:20:28,337 --> 00:20:30,506
Somebody has to get in there
and save Ophanimon.

414
00:20:30,506 --> 00:20:32,141
-I want to go, too.

415
00:20:32,174 --> 00:20:34,243
I mean, after all we've been
through, we should help fight

416
00:20:34,276 --> 00:20:35,911
the bully that caused
all of this, right?

417
00:20:35,945 --> 00:20:37,479
-Kid's got a point.

418
00:20:37,546 --> 00:20:39,381
And of course, if he goes, I
have to come along, too,

419
00:20:39,415 --> 00:20:40,716
because I'm the oldest.

420
00:20:40,749 --> 00:20:43,052
Besides, I've got to make sure
he stays out of trouble.

421
00:20:43,085 --> 00:20:45,354
-And I have no intention
of going home now.

422
00:20:45,387 --> 00:20:49,225
Can't let you boys have all
the fun now, can I?

423
00:20:49,225 --> 00:20:51,393
-We're coming and that's final.

424
00:20:51,393 --> 00:20:52,928
Yeah!

425
00:20:52,995 --> 00:20:56,232
NARRATOR: All for one
and one for-- wait!

426
00:20:56,232 --> 00:20:57,900
Are they out of their minds?

427
00:20:57,933 --> 00:21:01,570
Let's see if they survive this
one on the next Digimon

428
00:21:01,637 --> 00:21:03,672
Digital Monsters.

